div.div:
• ProductLicenseEntity contains immutable core license data
• LicenseActivityEntity tracks all changeable usage data and transactions
• Each license type uses specialized entities for specific functionality
• All entities inherit from AuditWorkflowEntity for comprehensive audit trails
• Multi-tenant architecture with tenant_id foreign keys on all entities
• Supports three license types: File-based, Product Key, and Volumetric licenses
